lead_paragraph: The Chicago Cubs set up a winner-take-all Game Seven of the World Series by crushing the Cleveland Indians 9-3 on Tuesday to level Major League Baseball's best-of-seven championship.

headline.print_headline: Cubs Crush Indians to Send World Series to Game 7
